[[unpartei/RepairRobot|RepairRobot]][[http://google.com/search?q=RepairRobot|➜°]] and [[unpartei/BasicIncome|BasicIncome]][[http://google.com/search?q=BasicIncome|➜°]]

Step1: The current [[unpartei/BMW|BMW]][[http://google.com/search?q=BMW|➜°]]-project trivializes repair work, thus allowing more doityourself work, setting free innumerous maintainance worker (not only in the automobile industry).

Step2: If any repair step (in complex machines) can be shown by an algorithm, than soon even the doityourself workers will become superfluous.

Result: a basic income for all people in the world becomes a necessity.

